757
00:40:06,130 --> 00:40:07,700
But only for today.

758
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:16,000
Straighten your backs.

759
00:40:20,610 --> 00:40:21,810
Go lower.

760
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:32,730
I think you have the team's fund card.

761
00:40:32,730 --> 00:40:34,250
