772
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:00,680
You're so lazy.

773
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:01,850
Zhong Zixuan.

774
00:41:01,870 --> 00:41:03,020
Squat lower.

775
00:41:04,370 --> 00:41:06,000
