784
00:42:00,220 --> 00:42:01,340
I've paid for

785
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:02,400
the uniform.

786
00:42:08,150 --> 00:42:09,510
Thank you.

787
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:10,910
I've booked

788
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:11,940
the hotel

789
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:13,070
